communitySectionDescription.message: We’ve teamed up with 10 community panelists to create a collection that represents 10 of the most impactful images on Unsplash from 2021. And now, we’d love to hear from you. Vote for the image that resonates most with you, and the one with the most votes will be selected for the Photo of 2021 Award.

descriptionPart1.message: The Unsplash Awards are a month-long celebration recognizing the powerful impact that the Unsplash community has made through their generosity and artistry. Unsplash wouldn’t exist without the thousands of contributors who freely gift their work and push creativity forward every day.

descriptionPart2.message: From the very best of architecture & interiors, to an all-new 3D category — enter your images into 11 categories designed to showcase the best of Unsplash. We’ve also invited amazing guest judges to help select the featured images for each category.

headTagsDescription.message: Yearly celebration of the best of open photography

howToParticipateListItem1.message: Select the category you’d like to participate in, and click Submit.

howToParticipateListItem2.message: You can either submit a new photo or choose a photo from your library.

howToParticipateListItem3.message: If choosing a photo from your library — only photos submitted after {onlyPhotosSubmittedAfter, date, long} will be eligible for this year’s Awards.

howToParticipateParagraph1.message: Note: All images that have been curated to the Awards topics between {awardsTopicAutomaticallySubmittedStart, date, long} and {awardsTopicAutomaticallySubmittedEnd, date, long} are automatically submitted to this year’s Awards. The number of eligible photos will be shown under the Submit button.

howToParticipateParagraph2.message: Read more about our rules and regulations <rulesAndRegulationsLink>here</rulesAndRegulationsLink>.

subTitle.message: Celebrating the best of open photography
